        "timestamp": "2021-08-25 14:46:41.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Agree, in that case sequencing can be made through a single file.\n\nYes, and I'm thinking sequencing would just be done based on the order of lines in the file rather than via an extra \"sequence\" column.  That would make it easy to add, remove, and move things around.",
